2 charter performance agreement may be revoked immediately.
3 3. A public charter school has thirty days to respond to the superintendent of public
4 instruction's notice to revoke the school's charter performance agreement.
5 4. If the superintendent of public instruction revokes or does not renew a charter
6 performance agreement, the superintendent of public instruction shall publish the
