1 e. Is a public entity under chapter 44 - 04 .
2 2. Individuals compensated by an education service provider are prohibited from serving
3 as a voting member on a governing board contracting with the education service
4 provider, except if approved by the superintendent of public instruction.
5 Public school employees.
6 1. Public charter school teachers must be licensed by the education standards and
7 practices board and must meet the requirements under chapter 15.1 - 18 .
8 2. An employee of a public charter school is eligible to participate in retirement and
9 benefits programs of the state, if the public charter school elects to participate and
